---
title: Sticky Haloumi, Beef Rump & Bombay Potatoes with Cucumber Salad & Garlic Aioli
description: Sweet chilli sauce is a crowd favourite and we want to put it on everything! Haloumi and beef is up next and once again, this sauce has outdone itself. The salty haloumi gets a little sweeter and the potatoes get a decadent sprinkling of Mumbai spice, what more could you ask for?
